{
  "texts": [
    "Each conv block has 3 Â 3 conv layers with 64 filters, batch normalization, ReLU nonlinearity, and 2 Â 2 max-pooling.",
    "ResNet architecturesResNet (Residual Network) architectures were proposed by He et al. [34].",
    "In this study, the proposed ResNet18, ResNet34, and ResNet50 architectures were used.",
    "These architectures differ from each other in terms of the number of layers, the number of conv layers in each residual block, and filter size.ResNet18 is the simplest version of ResNet, and it consists of 18 layers, including the input and output layers.",
    "It has 11.69 million parameters."
  ]
}